{"tid":339903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"忌廉哥fb論「割地」掀罵戰","createTime":"2017-07-29T12:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T12:33:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"477ea8c03dfafc8ffc5f222368b5e8aaa06ccd38","tid":339903,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20105226&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20105226%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170729&d=tFCJbJsiQRGJCN592fjRKDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e9e072fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20105226%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170729&h=22e21a95\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20105226&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170729</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要聞港聞兩岸國際娛 樂更多果 籽財 經體 育<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n忌廉哥fb論「割地」掀罵戰 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府提出將廣深港高鐵西九龍總站四分一樓層租畀內地管轄，實施一地兩檢，租界範圍司法管轄權全交內地，被指係割地，激起各界反響；明星貓「忌廉哥」fb日前亦抽水，po忌廉哥瞓覺相，配上文字「割了這片地 像割了我忽肉 我愛我城」，似乎係反對一地兩檢。<br />\n點知帖文一出，即被洗版留言大鬧專頁將貓政治化，唔少留言者個人圖像有「藍絲帶」。<br />\n另外，專頁亦不乏以簡體字留言者，大多批評版主利用忌廉哥宣揚政治，係「用貓過橋」，直轟「請勿利用大眾喜愛的忌廉哥作為政治工具」、又指「對忌廉的主人或者代筆寫這篇的人非常失望」。<br />\n但亦有唔少留言支持帖文，指香港係個有言論自由嘅地方，唔喜歡可unlike專頁，「又要like人哋個page，又接受唔到人哋想講嘅嘢係咩心態？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170729/large/29lp2p05new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170729%2Flarge%2F29lp2p05new.jpg&h=d4fd06cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n忌廉哥fb日前po咗瞓覺相論割地，引起熱議。忌廉哥fb圖片"}]}